}}[[Classes]]: [[Classes:SpecialSpot|SpecialSpot]]&rarr;<u>BossSpot</u>


[[Classes:Sorcerer2|D'Sparil]] randomly chooses one of the available BossSpots as a destination when he teleports after having been hurt. If no BossSpot is available, D'Sparil will never teleport. BossSpots should be spawned before D'Sparil himself is, otherwise he will never use them.

